g/uploads/20180727191038k6QoNwL2Zf9FT4uc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/343774/vans-zhecihuanhefangaomeishuguanhezuodailaileyizuxiekuan/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 与梵高美术馆推出合作系列</a></strong>。</p><p>系列中包含了 Sk8-Hi、Old Skool、Slip-On 以及 Authentic 等经典鞋型，印有《自画像》、《盛开的杏花》、《骷髅头》、《向日葵》等作品。除球鞋外，也有包括 Bomber 夹克、帽衫、T-Shirt、帽款及背包等单品。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191523ct2QLF4G0aKTuowU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600121\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807271915311UrJRuzcKXGM5wYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599768\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191552Zq7BjONvUxpCbDGy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191601N5Ro4mFMzagB2Cnx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600242\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191606jsxi7mHkY93F28dB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191612NJ0otORylqsbM3WH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599767\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191619aIAo1vyBn8sUbWTj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599644\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191628RhonV1tADIE98Hus.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191644kUM50NvGWymaSLX9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191654BPYbMwNzR6cyDLH2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180727191702RVd3pPX4e2ghY